title: LOOKING FOR PEOPLE TO DO A FRIENDLY CUSTOM 5V5 FOR FUN
body:
I'm looking for pretty much 5 people to do a friendly casual 5v5 or 4v4 or even 3v3.

It's just for fun. I already have my own team of 5 that's ready to verse. 

Add me: E Bubble

it can be any ranked. You also need skype to communicate for youse.
